<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bangalore IT Hub | Customer Feedback</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f5f7fb;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
min-height:100vh;
padding:20px;
}

.card{
background:#fff;
width:100%;
max-width:430px;
border-radius:18px;
padding:25px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}

.logo{
width:120px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

h2{
color:#0d6efd;
margin-bottom:8px;
}

p{
color:#555;
margin-bottom:18px;
}

.btn{
display:block;
width:100%;
padding:14px;
margin-top:12px;
border-radius:10px;
text-decoration:none;
font-size:16px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#fff;
transition:.3s;
}

.google{
background:#34A853;
}

.google:hover{
background:#2d9248;
}

.whatsapp{
background:#25D366;
}

.whatsapp:hover{
background:#20b85a;
}

.review-box{
margin-top:25px;
text-align:left;
}

.review-box h3{
margin-bottom:12px;
text-align:center;
}

.review{
background:#f8f8f8;
padding:12px;
border-radius:10px;
margin-bottom:10px;
cursor:pointer;
border:1px solid #ddd;
}

.review:hover{
background:#e8f5e9;
}

.copy{
margin-top:12px;
text-align:center;
color:green;
font-weight:bold;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<img src="logo.png" class="logo">

<h2>Bangalore IT Hub</h2>

<p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐<br>
Thank you for choosing us.<br>
Please share your valuable feedback.</p>

<a class="btn google"
href="https://g.page/r/CRIlXdVhFYvhEBM/review"
target="_blank">
⭐ Give Google Review
</a>

<a class="btn whatsapp"
href="https://wa.me/918618084202"
target="_blank">
💬 Chat on WhatsApp
</a>

<div class="review-box">

<h3>Review Suggestions</h3>

<div class="review" onclick="copy(this)">
Excellent CCTV products and quick installation service. Highly recommended!
</div>

<div class="review" onclick="copy(this)">
Best CCTV shop in Bangalore with genuine products and reasonable prices.
</div>

<div class="review" onclick="copy(this)">
Professional installation, excellent customer support and quality cameras.
</div>

<div class="review" onclick="copy(this)">
Best wholesale prices for CCTV products. Trusted supplier with fast service.
</div>

<div class="review" onclick="copy(this)">
Original products, friendly staff and on-time delivery. Fully satisfied.
</div>

<div id="msg" class="copy"></div>

</div>

</div>

<script>

function copy(e){

navigator.clipboard.writeText(e.innerText);

document.getElementById("msg").innerHTML="✅ Review copied successfully!";

}

</script>

</body>
</html>
